title: Jaycoinz
author: Jaycoinz
content: Nigeria has turn to a country with different drama every year, just imagine every year different acting of new scene, for instance       2020 the scene of lookdown (covid 19)      2021 the scene of end SAR      2022 the scene of blocking SIM      2023 the scene of new Naira.  Drama no dey tire us.Gotten from Facebook.
